arts.ttl: AFC Wimbledon maintain perfect home league form with victory against Morecambe
arts.sum: The Dons made it five wins from five in League Two, while Morecambe remain at the foot of the table following defeat.

AFC Wimbledon's 1-0 defeat to Notts County at the weekend made it three 1-0 defeats in their last five games. Morecambe's 2-1 defeat to MK Dons at the weekend made it just two wins in their last nine...
